
# clang编译taskflow

```shell

#安装clang-10
sudo apt-get install clang-10

# 修改默认c++编译器
update-alternatives --config c++

# 安装libc++
sudo apt-get install libc++-dev
sudo apt-get install libc++abi-dev

mkdir build && cd ./build

cmake -DCMAKE_CXX_STANDARD=17 -DCMAKE_CXX_STANDARD_REQUIRED=ON -DCMAKE_CXX_EXTENSIONS=OFF -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER_ID=Clang -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER_VERSION=10.0.0 -DCMAKE_CXX_STANDARD_COMPUTED_DEFAULT=17 -DCMAKE_CXX_EXTENSIONS_COMPUTED_DEFAULT=OFF -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`pwd`/installed  ../

make -j8

```